use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104agq1665703194991.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/agq1665703194991.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/agq1665703194991.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"agq1665703194991\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get static information about servers registered with the Uniface Router.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"agq1665703194991__section_upy_df2_gwb\">\n<p class=\"lines\" id=\"agq1665703194991__lines_jpl_2f2_gwb\"><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">operation GET_SERVERS</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">params</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Using</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C1)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Host</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C256)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">User</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C40)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">UST</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C20)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  entity URSERVERS.UROUTMON : OUT</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">endparams</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agq1665703194991__section_cmg_4f2_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1026327e105\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"agq1665703194991__ul_tkl_rf2_gwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Using</var>—code indicating how the servers are identified; one of: <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"agq1665703194991__ul_vkl_rf2_gwb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">S</code> for servers with the specified host name, UST, and/or user name. </li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">C</code> for servers used by clients with the specified host name, UST,and/or user\n              name. </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Host</var>—host name of the client or server. </li>\n<li class=\"li\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">User</var>—user name of the client or server. </li>\n<li class=\"li\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">UST</var>—Uniface Server Type (UST) of the client or server. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">URSERVERS.UROUTMON—multiple occurrences of entity URSERVERS.UROUTMON, containing server\n          information. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">URSERVERS.UROUTMON entity</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">Fieldname</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">Packing Code</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">srvid</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Unique server identification, primary key</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">pid</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Server process identification</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ust</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">C20</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Uniface server type (UST)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">user</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">C40</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">O/S user name</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">host</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">C256</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Host name / IP address</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">startstamp</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">E5</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">Datetime</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Server started at dd-mmm-yyyy hh:mm:ss</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">connet</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">C3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Connection network to Uniface Router (e.g.\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">TCP</code>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">conaddr</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">C8</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Connection address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port\n                number)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">server</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">C80</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Server or hop or 'Any' server, for\n                    example:<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ora:|u|p /ex /su</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">tcp:h|u|p</code> or\n                    <code class=\"ph codeph\">ANY</code></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">maxsrv</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Maximum servers for this UST</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">maxidle</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Maximum idle time, in seconds, for this UST</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">maxreq</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"agq1665703194991__table_qtt_4g2_gwb__entry__4\">Maximum number of requests for this UST</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The order of servers is undefined. The selection criteria <var class=\"keyword varname\">Host</var>,\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">User</var> and/or <var class=\"keyword varname\">UST</var>, if present, are combined (using\n        logical AND) and applied to running servers or clients to select the list of servers.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agq1665703194991__section_zzn_qg2_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1026327e433\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If successful, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to the number (&gt;=0) of returned\n        USERVERS occurrences. Otherwise, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html#qln1665702528769__section_fbt_4d2_gwb\">Return Codes</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agq1665703194991__section_rv2_vg2_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1026327e449\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agq1665703194991__section_sl2_wg2_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1026327e458\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">GET_SERVERS</span> operation gets static information about servers\n        registered with the Uniface Router.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525677\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525677\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "GET_SERVERS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get static information about servers registered with the Uniface Router. operation GET_SERVERS params string Using : IN ; (C1) string Host : IN ; (C256) string User : IN ; (C40) string UST : IN ; (C20) entity URSERVERS.UROUTMON : OUT endparams Parameters Using —code indicating how the servers are identified; one of: S for servers with the specified host name, UST, and/or user name. C for servers used by clients with the specified host name, UST,and/or user name. Host —host name of the client or server. User —user name of the client or server. UST —Uniface Server Type (UST) of the client or server. URSERVERS.UROUTMON—multiple occurrences of entity URSERVERS.UROUTMON, containing server information. Table 1. URSERVERS.UROUTMON entity Fieldname Packing Code Data Type Description srvid I4 Numeric Unique server identification, primary key pid I4 Numeric Server process identification ust C20 String Uniface server type (UST) user C40 String O/S user name host C256 String Host name / IP address startstamp E5 Datetime Server started at dd-mmm-yyyy hh:mm:ss connet C3 String Connection network to Uniface Router (e.g. TCP ) conaddr C8 String Connection address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port number) server C80 String Server or hop or 'Any' server, for example: ora:|u|p /ex /su or tcp:h|u|p or ANY maxsrv I4 Numeric Maximum servers for this UST maxidle I4 Numeric Maximum idle time, in seconds, for this UST maxreq I4 Numeric Maximum number of requests for this UST The order of servers is undefined. The selection criteria Host , User and/or UST , if present, are combined (using logical AND) and applied to running servers or clients to select the list of servers. Return Values If successful, $status is set to the number (>=0) of returned USERVERS occurrences. Otherwise, see Return Codes . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The GET_SERVERS operation gets static information about servers registered with the Uniface Router. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}